Definition: often followed by `as')
Example: they were equally beautiful; birds were singing and the child sang as sweetly; sang as sweetly as a nightingale; he is every bit as mean as she is
Synonyms: adj, all, equal, as, every_bit, to, the, same, degree, often, followed, by, they, were, beautiful, birds, singing, and, child, sang, sweetly, a, nightingale, he, is, every, bit, mean, she
Category: adv.all
